OPERATORS


operators are used to perform arthmetic logical & relational operation on operands or constants.
it determines a specific action or process.

operators are of few they are:
-- arthmetic operators => used to perform arthmetic operations
-- assignment operators => used to assign values to the variables
-- comparision operators => it is used in logical statement to determine the equality and diff between the variables or 
                            values
-- logical operators => used to determine the logic btw variables or values
-- conditional operators => the conditional statement is also known as Ternary operators.
                            the javascript evalutes the expression for true or false values and then executes the one 
                            of two given statements based on the results 